co.cask.cdap.api.templates

Interface AdapterConfigurer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AdapterPluginRegistry

    @Beta
public interface AdapterConfigurer
extends AdapterPluginRegistry
    Configurer used to configure program used in the execution of the Adapter. Currently, only Worker or Workflow can be used in the execution.

      • addDatasetType

        void addDatasetType(Class<? extends Dataset> datasetClass)
        Adds a DatasetModule to be deployed automatically during adapter creation if it does not already exist. Uses Dataset as a base for the DatasetModule. The module will have a single dataset type identical to the name of the class in the datasetClass parameter.
        Parameters:
        datasetClass - the class of the dataset, with the module name the same as the class in the parameter

      • createDataset

        void createDataset(String datasetName,

        Parameters:
        datasetName - the name of the dataset instance
        typeName - the name of the dataset type
        properties - the properties of the dataset instance

      • createDataset

        Parameters:

        datasetClass - dataset class to create the Dataset type from
